NOTE:
1. Copy main() source file to temp_app.c, then you can use Makefile.
2. Change the original main() source file to xxx_C for backup.  
3. Make it and you will get bin file temp_app, change the name as you wish.
4. Black_and_While font images show sharply in contrasting color backgroud, while Gray font images show softly
   and smoothly in simlar color backgroup.  When replace default font color with a given one, the Gray img font may 
   getting worse. that because all non-zero color vaule will be replaced by the SAME given value.
